metadata.name: Dreamy
metadata.description: Dreamy is a central meeting place for all adventurers, where it all begins. Invoking the feelings of togetherness and familiarity, with a sense of tranquillity and calmness. A place where there is no noise. Dreamy emerged from the idea of escaping the everyday noise of life, with the desire of immersing ourselves in a new world and forging lasting friendships. Dreamy begins with a series of 7,777 digital collectibles on the Ethereum blockchain.
